# Render Static Site SPA fallback.
# Format is the same as Netlify _redirects.
#
# `/* /index.html 200` tells Render: for ANY path that doesn't match a
# real file, serve /index.html with HTTP 200. This lets the Flutter
# router handle all client-side routes (e.g. /loginUni, /resetPasswordUni)
# instead of returning 404.
#
# This file MUST live in the published directory (build/web/_redirects).
# Render reads it at deploy time. We copy it into build/web after the
# Flutter build via build.sh.
/*    /index.html   200
